{"type": "article", "id": 8959, "title": "碳纤维台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-28T07:18:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235346DLGV47omZXf2PSn8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这款名为 “T°RED C7OLED” 的灯在米兰设计周“碳纤维与设计”专场进行了展出，它采用了大理石的底座，而灯架则是 88.5 厘米的悬挂长丝碳纤维，长丝碳纤维厚度为 4mm，重量则是 188 克，很好的保持了灯具的动感和平衡，上方装有两个 LED 灯泡，看上去简约而时尚。<a href=\"http://www.spaziotadini.it/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>能看到展会现场的情况。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235344cswuLUCNOz7byrm4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235344W5gykHAIRGmE2YJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235344q0slQHpO2fxPtmKC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64914425\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235345QvGbk1yRATNnZsx4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235345ouw12I4YSjaeKyET.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235345Y2umlQXSVB4sUvcn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69193154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}